OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FBen Kinsella's artwork, including a
OL,7,Fpiece he painted just three months
OL,8,Fbefore his death, is on display at
OL,9,FGrove Gallery in west London.
OL,11,FThe collection, running from March
OL,12,F17th to April 17th, features a letter
OL,13,FBen wrote to the Prime Minister just
OL,14,Fmonths before he was murdered in 2008.
OL,16,FITV News spoke to his sister, Brooke
OL,17,FKinsella, who attended the exhibition
OL,18,Fand left a handprint on a painting of
OL,19,Fdoves - symbols that Ben had used in
OL,20,Fhis GCSE artwork.
