OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FShe said: "Ben did so many wonderful
OL,7,Fart pieces,"
OL,9,F"One of the last things he did was
OL,10,Fthis bird symbol. Throughout history,
OL,11,Fthe bird has been a sign of hope and
OL,12,Fpeace, and that's what we try to do as
OL,13,Fa trust in his name - create peace for
OL,14,Fyoung people and give hope that we can
OL,15,Fmake a difference."
OL,17,FBen was 16 when he was stabbed while
OL,18,Fcelebrating the end of his exams in
OL,19,FIslington. He was the 17th teenager to
OL,20,Fbe killed in London that year.
