OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FBy the end of 2008, 29 young people
OL,7,Fhad lost their lives. The highest
OL,8,Fnumber of teenage killings was
OL,9,Frecorded in 2021, when 30 were
OL,10,Fmurdered.
OL,12,FBrooke said that 'it's really hard' to
OL,13,Fhear of others losing their lives to
OL,14,Fknife crime.
