OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FShe said: "Every time I hear that
OL,7,Fanybody is lost to knife crime, let
OL,8,Falone the younger generation, because
OL,9,Fas a family, we know every stage of
OL,10,Fwhat they will be going from - from
OL,11,Fgetting that very first phone call to
OL,12,Fwhat you then need to do in the
OL,13,Fimmediate aftermath of it.
OL,15,F"They're not just numbers and
OL,16,Fstatistics to us, they are people and
OL,17,Fwe know what the ones that are left
OL,18,Fbehind are going through. So it's
OL,19,Freally, really hard. It's hard."
