OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FBrooke was among the families of knife
OL,7,Fcrime victims who recently met the
OL,8,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer alongside
OL,9,Factor Idris Elba. They spoke about a
OL,10,Fletter Ben had written to then-Prime
OL,11,FMinister Gordon Brown, raising
OL,12,Fconcerns about youth violence.
OL,14,F"He was 16, and he said how worried he
OL,15,Fwas about our youth," she said.
OL,17,FSixteen years after her brother's
OL,18,Fdeath, Brooke said knife crime will
OL,19,Fonly end if everyone takes
OL,20,Fresponsibility.
