OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,F"There is no one answer. That much I
OL,7,Fknow. It takes a collective community.
OL,9,F"It takes everybody to come together
OL,10,Fto do their bit to stop this
OL,11,Fhappening. You can see the emotion in
OL,12,Fthese (art) pieces and actually,
OL,13,Fsometimes it might resonate with an
OL,14,Faudience in a way that other formats
OL,15,Fhaven't so far.
OL,17,F"So I think just trying anything we
OL,18,Fcan to get the message across is all
OL,19,Fwe can do."
