OL,3,C'We have to have hope': Ben Kinsella's
OL,4,Csister on her brother's legacy
OL,6,FBen had originally wanted to be an
OL,7,Factor but had set his sights on a
OL,8,Fcareer in graphic design.
OL,10,FHis work is now being featured in an
OL,11,Fexhibition by the artist Aidan Phelan,
OL,12,Fwhose own pieces explore darker themes.
OL,14,F"My work tells a slightly darker
OL,15,Fstory, but the great thing about this
OL,16,Fis we can put a positive note on
OL,17,Fsomething so negative. And that was
OL,18,FBen's message," he said.
